Debian Install PLank:

Download latest tar file:
 https://launchpad.net/plank

Download link on right.

Install dependencies:
sudo apt-get install automake gnome-common intltool pkg-config valac 
libbamf3-dev libdbusmenu-gtk3-dev libgdk-pixbuf2.0-dev 
libgee-dev libglib2.0-dev libgtk-3-dev libwnck-3-dev libx11-dev libgee-0.8-dev

go to where the file was saved.

untar the file (right click, "extract here")

cd into the new directory ( cd Downloads/plank-0.11.2 )
 
./configure
 
make
 
sudo make install

sudo ldconfig

add to autostart